30/08/2011

Development release (3.1.90)

- Updated POTFILES.in (Piotr Drąg)
        - Adapt configure for tracker-sparql. (Luis Medinas)
        - Use libtracker-sparql instead of libtracker-client since it's deprecated. Fixes bgo #651630. (Luis Medinas)
        - Updated Belarusian translation. (Ihar Hrachyshka)
        - Remove beagle from Brasero. Fixes bgo #657313 and #639257. (Luis Medinas)
        - Updated Japanese translation (OKANO Takayoshi)
