        - Updated Norwegian bokmål translation (Kjartan Maraas)
        - Revert "build: add checks for beagle libraryies to configure as it is used in the code" (Stefan Sauer)
        - build: add checks for beagle libraryies to configure as it is used in the code (Stefan Sauer)
        - Make Brasero build with tracker 0.10. 0.8 is older enough and shouldn't be available in any system with GNOME 3.2. 
	  This is a temporary fix until we move to tracker-sparql. (Luis Medinas)
        - Fix bgo #649178 - Wrong semi-colon in brasero-nautilus.desktop. (Luis Medinas)
        - Fix Documenters list in the About Dialog. Fixes bgo #646112. Added myself to Application authors (Luis Medinas)
        - Bump to 3.1.5. (Luis Medinas)
        - nautilus: wait for the track to load file info before adding to session (Cosimo Cecchi)
        - Updated Thai translation. (Theppitak Karoonboonyanan)
